      <div class="referral">
        <p>Deploy your next app in seconds. Get $100 in cloud credits:</p>
        <a href="https://www.digitalocean.com/?refcode=0e2c3672d1dc&utm_campaign=Referral_Invite&utm_medium=Referral_Program&utm_source=badge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
